    <body>
        <p MadCap:conditions="Version.14-2-born">By default, the Change API caches paths that are updated repeatedly in order to improve performance. However, this may increase memory consumption more than usual in certain cases, such as when the path is dynamic. To prevent memory leaks, you can disable the path caching. </p>
